<p>[2]Spears, W.T., Morphis II, J.G., Lester, S.G., Williams, S.D., Einhorn, L.H., 1992. Brain metastases and testicular tumors: long-term survival. International Journal of Radiation Oncology* Biology* Physics<em> </em>22, 17-22.</p>
